
Globally, if maximum-deceleration equals 5.0 and distance-to-preceding-vehicle-at-current-velocity less than distance-to-collision-threshold, then in response driver-warning-signal equals true and driver-warning-signal-duration equals 0.1 and driver-warning-signal-pause-duration equals 0.2.
Globally, if driver-warning-signal equals true, then in response driver-demand-to-intervene equals true.
